00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,081
Marvin!
马文!

181
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:33,206
- You're driving me crazy!  - I brought the key.
- 你快把我逼疯了!  - 我带钥匙来了

182
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,205
You faked your death.
你又装死

183
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:41,283
- Gotta go.  - Let's go.
- 该走了  - 我们走

184
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,761
Gotta go.
走吧

185
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:45,642
You have no idea what you put me through!
你知道这给我惹了多大麻烦吗!

186
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,919
Oh! Thank God, you're okay.
哦! 谢天谢地 你没事

187
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:52,921
No!
不!

188
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:56,761
- What are you doing here?  - Marvin brought me. From the house.
- 你来干什么?  - 马文带我来的 从安全房

189
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:01,079
Has everybody lost their mind?
难道所有人都疯了吗?

190
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:04,687
- Marv, you don't bring a girl like that here.  - I had to see if you were okay, didn't I?
- 马文 你不能把那样的女人扯进来  - 我总要知道你没事 对吧?

191
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,359
Honey!
宝贝!

192
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,169
- I thought...  - What?
- 我觉得...  - 怎么了?

193
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:12,842
Remember when we had that conversation about how you were gonna lay low?
记得我们说过你不能参与这些吗?

194
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:14,883
You don't get to tell me when to lay.
你也没说哪些不能参与

195
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:17,050
I mean, I'm not saying that.
我想说 我不是那个意思

196
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:21,164
Stop. Just don't. Just don't... No.
别说了 别说了 别... 不

197
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:24,125
- You're mad at me now?  - You treat me like a china doll.
- 你现在生我气了?  - 你对我像瓷娃娃一样

198
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:26,679
Frank, can I give you a little advice about women?
弗兰克 我能给你一些关于女人的建议吗?

199
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,841
No! Absolutely not!
不能! 完全不能!

200
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:30,039
Listen, you gotta ask yourself,
这样 你应该扪心自问

201
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:33,079
what is a girl like that doing with a guy like you?
一个那样的女人跟你这样一个货在一起图什么?

202
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,844
It ain't for your looks.
肯定不是因为你长得帅

203
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:37,884
You know, I will shoot you. I will shoot you in the liver.
听着 我要开枪了 打烂你的肝

204
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:47,119
Adventure, romance, danger, activities you can share as a couple.
冒险 浪漫 危险 行动 这才是你能为伴侣分享的东西

205
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,043
It's about you lying to me.
是你骗我的事

206
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:50,447
Frank...
弗兰克...

207
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:55,364
I was very touched that you cried at my funeral.
你在我的葬礼上哭我很感动

208
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,766
That's not true.
没有的事

209
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:08,924
I didn't cry at your funeral.
我在你葬礼没有哭

210
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:11,050
I'm no crier.
我从来不哭

211
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:20,927
Ninety-six hours ago, somebody posted a document on the Internet
九十六个小时之前 有人在网络上发布了一份文件

212
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:25,489
that said you and I took part in an operation called Nightshade back in '79.
称你我曾经在79年参与过一个叫"龙葵"的行动

213
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:27,559
That's why you fake died?
所以你才会装死?

214
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:30,086
Yeah. The chatter went through the roof.
是 这引起了极大关注

215
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:34,359
So everybody's after you for something they think you know
所以所有这些追你们的人认为你们知道一些

216
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:36,362
that you don't even know at all?
你们其实并不知道的事?

217
