219
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:47,199
Yeah, I'm not going anywhere.
不 我哪也不去

220
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:51,524
- Cash only. No calls. No contacts.  - Thanks. Look...
- 只花现金 别打电话 别联系  - 谢谢 这样...

