223
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:01,599
- Dusky?  - Dark, smoldering.
- 幽昧?  - 幽暗 烟熏的意思

224
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,250
I know what it means, Marvin.
我知道什么意思 马文

225
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:09,639
It's hard to be the kinda person I have to be right now
有你在场的情况下

226
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:13,281
and do the kinda things that I'm going to have to do while you're here.
我做不了我自己 也办不成该办的事

227
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:15,130
This is gonna be good for us.
这会对我们有好处的

228
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:16,879
What are we doing?
我们要做什么?

229
