Let's face it, Columbo, things were getting a little stale.
面对吧 可伦坡 一切都变了

230
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:24,119
Wow. Mommy just slapped Daddy at the dinner table.
喔 妈妈在饭桌上扇了爸爸一巴掌哇

231
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:32,839
Is there a human being in the trunk?
后备箱里有个人?

232
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:33,887
Yeah.
是

233
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,645
Who is it, Marvin?
是谁 马文?

234
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:42,802
He's a Senior Director of Military Intelligence.
他是军情六处的一位高级主管

235
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:47,208
I've been caramelizing his onions for a couple of days.
我已经折磨他好多天了

236
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,640
Caramelizing how?
怎么折磨?

237
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:52,323
With three tabs of acid and a lot of rats.
三勺酸液和很多老鼠

238
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,411
Dang!
啊!

239
00:17:55,780 --> 00:17:57,411
{\an8}五角大楼

240
00:17:56,200 --> 00:18:01,366
Eleven people dead. Five FBI. And the SecDef wants a briefing?
11个人死了 5个是联邦调查局的 国防部长想要一个简报?

241
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,649
You were brought in to contain this.
你是干嘛吃的

242
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:05,801
Calm down.
冷静点

243
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,162
I can't believe this is coming back on me after so many years.
我不信这么多年了 这件事还会找上我

244
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:11,639
General, Moses and Boggs have been completely isolated.
将军 摩西和博格斯已经被彻底孤立了

245
