One of our old assets has some real information.
我们有个线人提供了一些真实情报

609
00:44:23,080 --> 00:44:24,764
He needs to meet with us right now.
他现在要跟我们见面

610
00:44:26,640 --> 00:44:27,801
Nah.
不

611
00:44:28,920 --> 00:44:31,924
Frank, what are you doing? She's kryptonite. What are you doing?
弗兰克 你在干嘛? 她是你的克星 你在干嘛?

612
00:44:32,120 --> 00:44:34,282
- I'll handle it.  - Are you sure?
- 我能应付  - 你确定?

613
00:44:37,560 --> 00:44:38,607
Yeah.
嗯

614
00:44:41,320 --> 00:44:44,279
It's not okay. It's just some work.
不好意思 有点工作要做

615
00:44:44,280 --> 00:44:48,126
- No, it's not fun.  - Go. You and Svetlana, you work it out.
- 别这样 多没意思  - 去吧 和你的俄国情人工作去吧

616
00:44:48,480 --> 00:44:52,769
I promise you that I will be back in time for dinner.
我保证我准时回来陪你吃饭

617
00:44:55,120 --> 00:44:56,121
I'll be back.
我会回来的

618
00:45:01,600 --> 00:45:02,761
Keep her safe.
保护好她

619
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:12,609
What happened to us, Frank?
弗兰克 我们之间怎么了?

620
00:45:12,960 --> 00:45:14,371
- Well...  - Hmm.
- 这个...  - 嗯

