00:52:16,400 --> 00:52:22,009
Incarcerate, Cannot Execute. Who would they keep on ICE for 32 years?
监禁但不能处死 他们会把谁留在ICE长达三十二年呢?

709
00:52:24,280 --> 00:52:26,362
- Come on. Gotta go.  - Come on where? Oh!
- 快 得走了  - 去哪? 哦!

